{"tid":933801,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[召喚連狗] 發覺而家連狗對色情嘅定義定得好高","createTime":"2018-12-08T18:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T19:55:10.000Z","uid":199590,"like":50,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"571939822919f7206135d421fb78d532f4ddc3a0","tid":933801,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:16:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n<br />\n最近我都出咗唔少post 當中有唔少都係關於囡囡嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔少post都俾連狗搬咗落成人台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當中有啲post的而且確有出到bam圖 我認為搬呢個post落成人台嘅決定十分正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以下為該post之link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bPpkMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bPpkMS</a><br />\n<br />\n但值得留意嘅係我大部分嘅post都冇出到bam圖 <br />\n佢地只係著住泳衣或者內衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以下為該post之link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bPhApS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bPhApS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bQianS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bQianS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bQoGFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bQoGFS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bQyntS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bQyntS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bQFCQS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bQFCQS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bQOwvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bQOwvS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bQQeBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bQQeBS</a><br />\n<br />\n在此 我想請問連狗 以上嘅post邊度成人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n係咪著內衣或者泳衣就代表成人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n定只有成人先可以著內衣同泳衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假若連狗你話著內衣同泳衣就好色情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我敢問一句 是否所有沙灘 泳池都好色情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n是否所有內衣店都好色情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我希望連狗下次可以嘗試用藝術嘅目光欣賞啲靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好因為自己睇到個post之後勃起咗 就將呢個post定性為成人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span></span>"},{"pid":"f107763db439f38ead97b5a4bf48987543177721","tid":933801,"uid":170772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T19:03:42.000Z","msg":"首先要定義咩係成人台"},{"pid":"a3a8c23e8434fc656c8c40a626692279a67d7c3e","tid":933801,"uid":199590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f107763db439f38ead97b5a4bf48987543177721","tid":933801,"uid":170772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T19:03:42.000Z","msg":"首先要定義咩係成人台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T00:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁你覺得成人台嘅定義係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我認為成人台 =18禁嘅意思 起碼都要出過bam圖 或者有av先算係成人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e392b7f608f675057ea37ae7a0e2c21f5fcd2e","tid":933801,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T00:57:20.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"6a84e036f800022e45164ef7937ab999bc4eb0ce","tid":933801,"uid":99568,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T00:58:53.000Z","msg":"我係連9分身<br />\n而家要ban你"},{"pid":"536f4653e499745af97d3f9996a3a660e8790606","tid":933801,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a84e036f800022e45164ef7937ab999bc4eb0ce","tid":933801,"uid":99568,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T00:58:53.000Z","msg":"我係連9分身<br />\n而家要ban你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim